trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> class represents a connection to a DSML Gateway using SOAP over HTTP.
trans-unit.target: La clase <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> representa una conexión a una puerta de enlace DSML que utiliza SOAP sobre HTTP.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="identifier" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="identifier" /> es una referencia nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="authType" /> value is not one of the DSML supported values.
trans-unit.target: El valor <paramref name="authType" /> no es ninguno de los valores admitidos para DSML.

trans-unit.source: DSML only supports Anonymous, Ntlm, Basic, Negotiate and digest.
trans-unit.target: DSML sólo admite la autenticación de negociación, anónima, NTLM, básica e implícita.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="authType" /> value is not one of the constants defined in the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: El valor <paramref name="authType" /> no es ninguna de las constantes definidas en la enumeración <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" />.

trans-unit.target: Valor de petición: <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityAction.Demand" />

trans-unit.source: An object derived from <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> that references the asynchronous request.
trans-unit.target: Objeto derivado de <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> que hace referencia a la solicitud asincrónica.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.Abort(System.IAsyncResult)" /> method cancels the asynchronous request.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.Abort(System.IAsyncResult)" /> cancela la solicitud asincrónica.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="asyncResult" /> is null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="asyncResult" /> es null (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="asyncResult" /> was not returned by the corresponding call to <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" />.
trans-unit.target: La llamada a <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" /> correspondiente no devolvió <paramref name="asyncResult" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.AuthType" /> property contains one of the values of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> enumeration that specifies the authentication type.
trans-unit.target: La propiedad <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.AuthType" /> contiene uno de los valores de la enumeración <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> que especifica el tipo de autenticación.

trans-unit.source: One of the values of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> enumeration that specifies the authentication type.
trans-unit.target: Uno de los valores de la enumeración <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> que especifica el tipo de autenticación.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> object to send.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> que se va a enviar.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AsyncCallback" /> function.
trans-unit.target: Función <see cref="T:System.AsyncCallback" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Object" /> that contains the state data for this request.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Object" /> que contiene los datos de estado de esta solicitud.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" /> method begins asynchronously sending the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> object to the server.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" /> empieza a enviar el objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> especificado al servidor de forma asincrónica.

trans-unit.source: An object derived from <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> that references the asynchronous send.
trans-unit.target: Objeto derivado de <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> que hace referencia al envío asincrónico.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="request" /> is null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="request" /> es null (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSession" /> method instructs the DSML server to start a new session.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSession" /> indica al servidor DSML que inicie una nueva sesión.

trans-unit.source: The method will block while waiting for a response from the DSML server and will time out according to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: El método se bloquea mientras espera una respuesta del servidor DSML y superará el tiempo de espera según el <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when a session is already open on the connection.
trans-unit.target: Se produce cuando ya hay una sesión abierta en la conexión.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when the XML returned from the Server in response to the <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSession" /> is not well-formed.
trans-unit.target: Se produce cuando el XML devuelto desde el servidor como respuesta a <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSession" /> no tiene un formato correcto.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when there is a communications failure with the DSML server or when the server is out of available sessions.
trans-unit.target: Se produce cuando hay un error de comunicación con el servidor DSML o cuando el servidor está fuera de las sesiones disponibles.

trans-unit.source: An object derived from <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> that contains state data for this request.
trans-unit.target: Objeto derivado de <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> que contiene datos de estado para esta solicitud.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.EndSendRequest(System.IAsyncResult)" /> method completes an asynchronous send request.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.EndSendRequest(System.IAsyncResult)" /> finaliza una solicitud de envío asincrónica.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlResponseDocument" /> object that contains the results of the request.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlResponseDocument" /> que contiene los resultados de la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when <paramref name="asyncResult" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Se produce cuando <paramref name="asyncResult" /> es <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Thrown if <paramref name="asyncResult" /> was not returned by the current instance from a call to <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" />.
trans-unit.target: Se produce si la instancia actual no devuelve <paramref name="asyncResult" /> de una llamada a <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" />.

trans-unit.source: The request did not complete.
trans-unit.target: La solicitud no finalizó.

trans-unit.source: No stream is available.
trans-unit.target: No hay ninguna secuencia disponible.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when the response returned by server is not valid.
trans-unit.target: Se produce cuando la respuesta devuelta por el servidor no es válida.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when abort was previously called or when an error occurred while processing the request.
trans-unit.target: Se produce si se ha ejecutado previamente una operación de anulación o si se produce un error al procesar la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.EndSession" /> method ends the session with the DSML server and clears the <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId" /> property.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.EndSession" /> finaliza la sesión con el servidor DSML y borra la propiedad <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId" />.

trans-unit.source: The method will block while waiting for a response from the DSML server and will time out according to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: El método se bloquea mientras espera una respuesta del servidor DSML y superará el tiempo de espera según el <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: If the DSML server has already terminated the session on its own, a <xref:System.Net.WebException> will be thrown.
trans-unit.target: Si el servidor DSML ya ha finalizado la sesión por sí solo, un <xref:System.Net.WebException> se iniciará.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId%2A> is still valid after the exception is thrown, the request never reached the server and the connection is still considered valid.
trans-unit.target: Si el <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId%2A> sigue siendo válido después de que se produce la excepción, la solicitud nunca ha llegado al servidor y la conexión todavía se considera válida.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when there is a communications failure with the DSML server.
trans-unit.target: Se produce cuando se produce un error de comunicación con el servidor DSML.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when there is no open session.
trans-unit.target: Se produce cuando no hay ninguna sesión abierta.

trans-unit.source: Sends an object to the DSML server.
trans-unit.target: Envía un objeto al servidor DSML.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest" /> object that contains the request.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest" /> que contiene la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest)" /> method sends a single <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest" /> object.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest)" /> envía un solo objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse" /> object that contains the results of the request.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse" /> que contiene los resultados de la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="request" /> is null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="request" /> es null (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The DSML server returned an error response.
trans-unit.target: El servidor DSML devolvió una respuesta de error.

trans-unit.source: The operation returned a failure code.
trans-unit.target: La operación devolvió un código de error.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> object sent to the server.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> enviado al servidor.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument)" /> method sends a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> object to the DSML server.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument)" /> envía un objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> al servidor DSML.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlResponseDocument" /> object that contains the results of the request.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlResponseDocument" /> que contiene los resultados de la solicitud.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="request" /> is null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="request" /> es null (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId" /> property contains the active session ID.
trans-unit.target: La propiedad <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId" /> contiene el id. de la sesión activa.

trans-unit.source: The active session ID.
trans-unit.target: Id. de la sesión activa.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SoapActionHeader" /> property contains the SOAP Action Header sent with other HTTP headers.
trans-unit.target: La propiedad <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SoapActionHeader" /> contiene el encabezado de acción SOAP enviado con otros encabezados HTTP.

trans-unit.source: The SOAP Action Header sent with other HTTP headers.
trans-unit.target: Encabezado de acción SOAP enviado con otros encabezados HTTP.

trans-unit.source: The default value of this property is "#batchRequest".
trans-unit.target: El valor predeterminado de esta propiedad es "#batchRequest".

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.Timeout" /> property contains the length of time, in seconds, before the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> times out.
trans-unit.target: La propiedad <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.Timeout" /> contiene los segundos que transcurren antes de que se agote <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" />.

trans-unit.source: The length of time, in seconds, before the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> times out.
trans-unit.target: Período de tiempo, en segundos, hasta que se agota <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" />.
